  EM iteration 1: max_change=0.099999 lambda=0.107128
  EM iteration 2: max_change=0.000016 lambda=0.107143
  EM iteration 3: max_change=0.000000 lambda=0.107143
splink: EM converged in 3 iterations, lambda=0.107143
splink: 3 matches, 5 clusters

